(m) Customer service and technical support;

(n) Human resource management and systems;

(o) Architecture services and other professional services through the internet;

(p) Management of teams of remote workers, and other competencies needed by companies and individuals pursuant to the full implementation of Republic Act No. 11165,

otherwise known as the "Telecommuting Act"; and

(q) Such other skills requirements as may evolve or be identified by the partners.
